### 0c — Navigate to the assignment via Courses

**CRITICAL: NEVER use the To-Do list. ALWAYS navigate via Courses.**

#### 0c-i — Click "Courses" in the main navigation

```javascript
(async () => {
  const d = ms => new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, ms));
