## Step 1 — Read the current question

```javascript
(async () => {
  const d = ms => new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, ms));
  await d(200);
  return JSON.stringify({
    title:    document.title,
    progress: document.querySelector('[class*="concept"]')?.innerText?.trim(),
    body:     document.body.innerText.substring(0, 1800)
  });
})()
```

Parse `body` to extract:
- **Progress** — `"N of 20 Concepts completed"`
- **Type** — `Multiple Choice Question` / `True or False Question` / `Multiple Select Question`
- **Stem** — the question text
- **Options** — all answer choices

Calculate target concepts from progress denominator:
`target = Math.ceil(total × pct)` e.g. 65% of 20 = 13.

