## Step 5 — Output: compact study-key table

```markdown
| Q# | Type  | Correct Answer |
|----|-------|----------------|
| Q1 | MCQ   | **Answer text** — one-line rationale |
| Q2 | T/F   | **TRUE** — one-line rationale |
| Q3 | Multi | **A & C** — one-line rationale |
```

Rules:
- Answers only — do **not** re-state the full question
- One-line rationale per row (≤ 12 words)
- Mark wrong-then-corrected answers with *(re-queued)* if applicable

