## Edge Cases

| Situation | Fix |
|-----------|-----|
| `clickOpt` doesn't match | Widen partial text; use exact wording from `body` |
| High button not clickable | Answer didn't register; re-click option, wait 300 ms, retry |
| Progress didn't advance | Concept needs another correct answer; keep answering |
| Page still shows "Answer Mode" | Previous Next didn't fire; click Next again |
| Tips modal blocks Q1 | Click "Got It" in Step 0d |
| "Courses" link not found in nav | Use fallback URL: `newconnect.mheducation.com/student/courses` |
| Course not found in list | Take screenshot; ask user to confirm course name |
| Assignment not visible on first screen | Scroll 320px up to 8 times before giving up |
| Assignment still not found after scrolling | Screenshot; ask user to confirm exact assignment name |
| Blue arrow click lands on summary page | Look for a second blue arrow / "Begin" / "Continue" button on that page and click it |
| No arrow/icon button found in row | Fall back to last clickable element in the row; never click the assignment name text |
| Sign In button not found on login page | Use attribute selectors as fallback; never ask the user to click it manually |
| SSO / university redirect | Wait up to 15 s for SSO to complete; do NOT ask user to log in |
| Autofill dropdown doesn't appear after `computer` click | Click the field again; wait 2 s; if still empty after 2 tries, take screenshot and ask user to click the email field once themselves to activate Chrome autofill, then resume |
| CAPTCHA / bot detection | **Only exception**: tell user once, wait for solve, then resume |

